tafsir[3]{c,v,t}:
  33,8,"That (Allah) may question the (custodians) of Truth concerning the Truth they (were charged with): And He has prepared for the Unbelievers a grievous Penalty."
  33,11,"In that situation were the Believers tried: they were shaken as by a tremendous shaking."
  33,12,"And behold! The Hypocrites and those in whose hearts is a disease (even) say: \"Allah and His Messenger promised us nothing but delusion!\""